{"sn5.8:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 5.8 ","sn5.8:0.2":"1. Bhikkhunivagga ","sn5.8:0.3":"Sisupacalasutta ","sn5.8:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn5.8:1.2":"Atha kho sisupacala bhikkhuni pubbanhasamayam nivasetva …pe… ","sn5.8:1.3":"annatarasmim rukkhamule divaviharam nisidi. ","sn5.8:1.4":"Atha kho maro papima yena sisupacala bhikkhuni tenupasankami; upasankamitva sisupacalam bhikkhunim etadavoca: ","sn5.8:1.5":"“kassa nu tvam, bhikkhuni, pasandam rocesi”ti? ","sn5.8:1.6":"“Na khvaham, avuso, kassaci pasandam rocemi”ti. ","sn5.8:2.1":"“Kam nu uddissa mundasi, ","sn5.8:2.2":"Samani viya dissasi; ","sn5.8:2.3":"Na ca rocesi pasandam, ","sn5.8:2.4":"Kimiva carasi momuha”ti. ","sn5.8:3.1":"“Ito bahiddha pasanda, ","sn5.8:3.2":"ditthisu pasidanti te; ","sn5.8:3.3":"Na tesam dhammam rocemi, ","sn5.8:3.4":"te dhammassa akovida. ","sn5.8:4.1":"Atthi sakyakule jato, ","sn5.8:4.2":"buddho appatipuggalo; ","sn5.8:4.3":"Sabbabhibhu maranudo, ","sn5.8:4.4":"sabbatthamaparajito. ","sn5.8:5.1":"Sabbattha mutto asito, ","sn5.8:5.2":"sabbam passati cakkhuma; ","sn5.8:5.3":"Sabbakammakkhayam patto, ","sn5.8:5.4":"vimutto upadhisankhaye; ","sn5.8:5.5":"So mayham bhagava sattha, ","sn5.8:5.6":"tassa rocemi sasanan”ti. ","sn5.8:6.1":"Atha kho maro papima “janati mam sisupacala bhikkhuni”ti dukkhi dummano tatthevantaradhayiti. "}